trans-unit.source: Represents a control that can be used to present a collection of objects on a design surface.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en kontroll som kan brukes til å finnes en samling av objekter i en utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: The WorkflowItemsPresenter is the second key [!INCLUDE[avalon1](~/add/includes/avalon1-md.md)] control provided by the [!INCLUDE[wf2](~/add/includes/wf2-md.md)] designer infrastructure that is collection based.
trans-unit.target: WorkflowItemsPresenter er den andre nøkkelen [!INCLUDE[avalon1](~/add/includes/avalon1-md.md)] kontrollen som er angitt av den [!INCLUDE[wf2](~/add/includes/wf2-md.md)] Spørringsutformer infrastruktur som er basert samling.

trans-unit.source: While the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemPresenter> enables the display and the editing of a single contained element, the WorkflowItemsPresenter is collection based, displays a visualization, and supports editing of the collection of items provided by the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemsPresenter.Items%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Mens den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemPresenter>aktiverer visning og redigering av ett enkelt inneholder element i WorkflowItemsPresenter er samling basert viser en visualisering og støtter redigering av samlingen av elementer fra den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemsPresenter.Items%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemsPresenter.Items%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemPresenter>

trans-unit.source: In addition to allowing the multiple items contained in the collection to be visualized and edited, the `WorkflowItemsPresenter` also enables collection-oriented actions, such as inserting an item at a given index in the collection, deleting an item from the collection, and moving an item from one index to another.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg til å tillate flere elementer i samlingen visualiseres og redigert, den `WorkflowItemsPresenter` kan også samlingen orientert handlinger, for eksempel sette inn et element på en angitt indeks i samlingen, slette et element fra samlingen og flytte et element fra én indeks til en annen.

trans-unit.source: `WorkflowItemsPresenter` also handles combined actions, such as dragging between the various presenters and allowing that edit to occur in a single, undoable action.Use <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemPresenter> to present a single object on a design surface.
trans-unit.target: `WorkflowItemsPresenter`håndtak kombineres også handlinger, for eksempel å dra mellom ulike Konferansestyrere og tillater at Rediger kan forekomme i et enkelt, kan angres handlingen. Bruk <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemPresenter>presentere ett enkelt objekt i en utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemPresenter>

trans-unit.source: For an example of the WorkflowItemsPresenter in use, see the [Custom Composite Designers - Workflow Items Presenter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) sample.
trans-unit.target: Et eksempel på WorkflowItemsPresenter i bruk, kan du se den [egendefinerte sammensatte utviklere - arbeidsflyten elementer Presenter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) utvalg.
